{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep this property set to "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}]},{"name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","type":"aside"}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)scalesWithViewingDistance","title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L180"}},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance","fragments":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tilted map."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationImage"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation"}}}